</span><span class='line'><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p></p>

<p>3.在Google-Font目录下新建一个css文件命名为google-font.css</p>

<pre><code>source/stylesheets/Google-Font/google-font.css
